            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Although https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/23581 would remove the need for this, I suppose we could mush this into here for now. But I would suggest naming it `tabpage`, not `id`.\n```suggestion\n      KeyValuePair pairs[] = { { .key = cstr_as_string(\"tabpage\"), .value = INTEGER_OBJ(handle) } };\n```",
            "commit_id": "8f1614d955d229cb6103ca189467eac4ba0c833f",
            "created_at": "2026-04-25T21:37:56Z",
