        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "> Oh right, thanks for calling that out. In that case it seems like `.tab` should be part of the `:help event-args` (`ev.tab` as opposed to `ev.data.tab`), i.e. we should promote this to a more standard field.\r\n> \r\n> Are you up for looking into that? It doesn't need to work for all events, but at least getting a routine in place would be worthwhile.\r\n\r\nMakes sense, so like how `ev.buf` works today where some autocommand sources provide it? I'll take a look at doing that.",
